DISTRIBUTION.—The species has an extensive range being reported from Argentina , Brazil , Colombia , Costa Rica , Ecuador , French Guiana, Guatemala , Honduras , Mexico , Nicaragua , Panamá , Peru , and Venezuela ( Metcalf 1963a ; Duffels & van der Laan 1985 ; Sanborn 2011a; 2013; 2014a; 2018c; 2019b; 2020b; Sanborn & Maes 2012 ;
Maes et al. 2012
; Sanborn & Heath 2014 ) with recent records expanding the distribution to Bolivia ( Sanborn 2019b ). Goding (1925) reported the species from Baños, Tungurahua province.
